{"tid":727951,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"試食超市食物","createTime":"2018-07-03T11:53:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T03:02:33.000Z","uid":182334,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8e4c8551c52292437c77cd8dab1c4f3ae893d50d","tid":727951,"uid":182334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T11:53:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/195317_d2339ec1f03d7d55a9ae6b2b0aa41a1b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F195317_d2339ec1f03d7d55a9ae6b2b0aa41a1b.JPG&h=8b183a54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/195318_67e4dc87cd3873c69d58790ec32a74ca.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F195318_67e4dc87cd3873c69d58790ec32a74ca.JPG&h=e0347ad4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nServing per container=2<br />\n不過我都係一口氣食完。<br />\n一開罐係凝固物，食咗啖感覺噁心，叮完兩分鐘變成極杰嘅芡狀物，小小鹹有啲粟米味，不過不失，但係始終似芡而唔係似粟米濃湯，配白飯會較好。<br />\n<br />\n賣相：5<br />\n口感：4<br />\n味道：5<br />\n總分：5"},{"pid":"2515a072f3c695ac3bfc64a9ddcb474d5cb29251","tid":727951,"uid":53254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T11:54:40.000Z","msg":"5分滿分?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031b3401886e2c5df5b4b0d5d2b91a8a7bedf4bb","tid":727951,"uid":182334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2515a072f3c695ac3bfc64a9ddcb474d5cb29251","tid":727951,"uid":53254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T11:54:40.000Z","msg":"5分滿分?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T11:57:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 十分滿分"},{"pid":"8393f7a2c725f30e2494d4c1cad1984b247c4df0","tid":727951,"uid":176063,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T12:08:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82ee43fe7334ce92cef57ddfe3d929607a3904c4","tid":727951,"uid":182334,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T13:50:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/213719_b20eb775b54920dda91ff3fb3c5c8e76.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F213719_b20eb775b54920dda91ff3fb3c5c8e76.JPG&h=23eddbfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢隻透明咖啡，飲落去有啲飲椰青嘅感覺，偏甜嘅咖啡味，飲完嘅update其實有少少似食完咖啡糖咁，質感稀過普通咖啡，但係亦都會feel到有奶嘅感覺。試吓ok,午後好飲好多<br />\n<br />\n賣相：5<br />\n口感：5<br />\n味道：7<br />\n總分：6"},{"pid":"b6ebfaf7a9cc59b264e4b86de96e99ea58173907","tid":727951,"uid":145071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8393f7a2c725f30e2494d4c1cad1984b247c4df0","tid":727951,"uid":176063,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T12:08:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T18:03:41.000Z","msg":"應該係加水煮粟米湯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a0558ca0835445435595882b6ece89d5a3cb735","tid":727951,"uid":3068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6ebfaf7a9cc59b264e4b86de96e99ea58173907","tid":727951,"uid":145071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8393f7a2c725f30e2494d4c1cad1984b247c4df0","tid":727951,"uid":176063,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T12:08:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T18:03:41.000Z","msg":"應該係加水煮粟米湯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T22:55:26.000Z","msg":"咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21b884c87da0daa5eb82623d8bf0d3f3c6958ccf","tid":727951,"uid":14250,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T23:04:46.000Z","msg":"金寶湯會唔會就咁食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb83c5957a274a6526cee4d3ebf497172f8e3a9","tid":727951,"uid":182334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T02:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/08/103733_51ea0aec31ab8b3bbb85065e765a5383.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F08%2F103733_51ea0aec31ab8b3bbb85065e765a5383.png&h=238056a1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/08/103734_b2b2905e8afb80c9dd4857ce2bc188c9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F08%2F103734_b2b2905e8afb80c9dd4857ce2bc188c9.png&h=582bfa60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n德國腸，每條平均8-10蚊，腸衣唔似司華力腸咁脆，肉質亦冇普通雞肉腸咁彈，有佢自己特別嘅味道，好難形容，都唔算令人難忘，可能係因為呢啲係日常食物, 所以味道唔會做到咁出<br />\n<br />\n賣相：5<br />\n口感：4<br />\n味道：6<br />\n總分：5"},{"pid":"6cdd5b43c494dfe431b0104576bbdec9ee02999d","tid":727951,"uid":33033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T03:02:33.000Z","msg":"開個blog 寫好過啦"}]}